Brightcove,is,an,online,digital,media,platform,used,by,media,companies,businesses,and,organizations,worldwide,to,publish,and,distribute,video,on,the,Web,The,on,demand,platform,is,used,by,professional,publishers,to,power,online,video,initiatives,The,Brightcove,Media,API,allows,users,to,interact,with,their,Brightcove,Media,Library,This,API,uses,REST,and,JavaScript,protocols,Responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON